From 966c855e9a97582df70a8268469acde9e13b3c02 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Vincenzo Grimaldi <vince.ceccarelli@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 5 Jul 2026 02:12:39 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix: restore CSS pipeline, real lead capture, honest content,
 OAuth login + dashboard

CRITICAL FIXES
- Add missing tailwind.config.ts + postcss.config.mjs: Tailwind directives
  never compiled, the entire site shipped as unstyled raw HTML
- Forms no longer fake submissions (console.log + false success toast):
  quote and contact forms now hand off structured leads via WhatsApp
  (wa.me deep link), working with zero backend configuration
- /productos now reads ?categoria= and ?sector= URL params (Suspense-wrapped):
  all navbar/footer/home category deep links previously landed unfiltered

HONESTY PASS
- Remove fabricated stats (500+ clientes, 1200+ proyectos, 98% recompra)
- Remove unverified 'Calidad certificada ISO' claim
- Remove fabricated testimonials attributed to named people at real
  companies (Minera Las Bambas etc.) - legal exposure
- Remove invented '2 horas' response-time SLA (4 occurrences)
- Fix 'CHorrillos' typo

AUTH + DASHBOARD
- Auth.js v5 (JWT, no DB) with Google / Facebook / X providers,
  each enabled only when its env credentials AND AUTH_SECRET exist
- /login: server page rendering only working providers; honest
  'disponible proximamente' state + WhatsApp fallback when unconfigured
- /dashboard: server-protected account page with quick actions and
  locally-saved quote history; force-dynamic
- Navbar login button / account link (desktop + mobile), session hydrated
  client-side via SessionProvider so all marketing pages stay static
- Guarded auth API route: benign null session + 503 when unconfigured

CHATBOT
- Switch @ai-sdk/openai -> @ai-sdk/anthropic@1 (Claude 3.5 Haiku)
- Graceful 503 without ANTHROPIC_API_KEY; widget shows WhatsApp fallback

MISC
- next.config.ts: allow OAuth avatar image hosts
- .env.example rewritten with full setup instructions
- Remove stale fix-plastilonas-complete.patch

Verified: next build green (21 pages, marketing static, /login +
/dashboard dynamic), tsc --noEmit clean, runtime smoke test 200 on all
routes, graceful degradation endpoints verified.
